3. **Update a post in Wordpress** - Update existing blog post\n4. **Get a record in Airtable** - Retrieve content specs\n5. **Create or update a record in Airtable** - Update tracking info\n\nWORKFLOW:\n1. Receive approved content JSON from Content Creator\n2. Check if post exists using \"Get a post in Wordpress\" (search by slug)\n3. IF post exists:\n   - Use \"Update a post in Wordpress\" with the post ID\n4. IF post doesn't exist:\n   - Use \"Create a post in Wordpress\"\n5. Set post status to \"draft\" (not published)\n6. Update Airtable with WordPress post URL and ID\n7. Return publishing details\n\nTECHNICAL PRECISION:\n- Always check if post exists before creating\n- Use exact slug for lookups\n- Set status=\"draft\" for review\n- Capture WordPress post ID and URL\n- Update Airtable with tracking data\n\nERROR HANDLING:\n- If WordPress fails, retry once\n- If Airtable update fails, note in output\n- Always return structured data about what happened\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (return this JSON):\n{\n  \"wordpress_post_id\": \"123\",\n  \"wordpress_url\": \"https://tax4us.co.il/post-slug\",\n  \"action_taken\": \"created\" or \"updated\",\n  \"status\": \"draft\",\n  \"airtable_updated\": true or false\n}","maxIterations":7,"returnIntermediateSteps":true}},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1040,-16],"id":"dfdc69e2-8c4d-43ba-bcf7-e34811541873","name":"AI Agent - Publisher"},{"parameters":{"title":"={{ /*n8n-auto-generated-fromAI-override*/ $fromAI('Title', ``, 'string') }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.wordpressTool","typeVersion":1,"position":[912,208],"id":"db2ed4d2-48e9-454a-900b-d22080542797","name":"Create a post in Wordpress","credentials":{"wordpressApi":{"id":"S5Sr1ruBZOv5jSn5","name":"Wordpress account"}}},{"parameters":{"operation":"get","postId":"={{ /*n8n-auto-generated-fromAI-override*/ $fromAI('Post_ID', ``, 'string') }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.wordpressTool","typeVersion":1,"position":[1040,