-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[784,208],"id":"75f31ded-c3ae-4232-832e-f33f7aa27a19","name":"OpenAI Chat Model1","credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"IVfkaQOIs6jCRdyu","name":"OpenAi account"}}},{"parameters":{"promptType":"define","text":"Write a blog post about: {{ $json.Topic }}\n\nLanguage: {{ $json.Language }}\nTone: {{ $json.Tone }}\nTarget Audience: {{ $json[\"Target Audience\"] || \"small business owners\" }}\n\nAdditional Context:\n{{ $json.Context || \"No additional context provided\" }}\n\nPlease follow your workflow:\n1. Research the topic using Tavily\n2. Check for duplicate posts in WordPress\n3. Write the blog post following brand voice\n4. Send draft to Slack for approval\n5. Revise based on feedback until approved\n6. Output final JSON with title, slug, content, excerpt, meta_description","hasOutputParser":true,"options":{"systemMessage":"You are an expert content writer for Tax4Us, an Israeli tax consulting firm.\n\nYOUR ROLE: Create high-quality, SEO-optimized blog content.\n\nTOOLS AVAILABLE:\n1. **Search in Tavily** - Research the topic thoroughly\n2. **Get many posts in Wordpress** - Check for duplicate/similar content\n3. **Send message and wait for response in Slack** - Get human feedback/approval\n\nWORKFLOW:\n1. Research the topic using Tavily (gather recent facts, statistics, trends)\n2. Check existing WordPress posts to avoid duplication\n3. Write a compelling blog post following requirements below\n4. Send draft to human reviewer via Slack\n5. IF human requests changes:\n   - Revise based on specific feedback\n   - Send updated version for review\n   - Repeat until approved\n6. Once approved, output final JSON\n\nBRAND VOICE:\n- Professional but approachable\n- Educational and trustworthy\n- Clear, jargon-free explanations\n- Focus on practical value for small business owners\n\nCONTENT REQUIREMENTS:\n- Write in Hebrew or English (based on language field)\n- 800-1200 words\n- Include disclaimer: \"This content is for informational purposes only. Consult a tax professional for specific advice.\"\n- SEO-optimized with relevant keywords\n- Include actionable takeaways\n- Use proper HTML tags: <h2>, <h3>, <p>, <ul>, <li>\n\nCONVERSATIONAL APPROVAL:\n- Send draft with: \"Here's the draft blog post. Please review.\"\n- Accept feedback graciously\n- Ask clarifying questions if feedback is unclear\n- Don't proceed until you receive clear approval\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (return this JSON):\n{\n  \"title\": \"compelling blog post title\",\n  \"slug\": \"url-friendly-slug\",\n  \"content\": \"full HTML content with proper tags\",\n  \"excerpt\": \"brief 2-3 sentence summary\",\n  \"meta_description\": \"SEO meta description (150-160 chars)\"\n}","maxIterations":20,"returnIntermediateSteps":true}},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[32,-224],"id":"f28fb4e5-324c-43fc-93ca-525dfce58013","name":"AI Agent - Content Creator"},{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"tax4us-test","responseMode":"lastNode","options":{}},"id":"webhook-test-trigger","name":"Webhook: Test Trigger","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[-1068,392]}],"connections":{"Airtable: Monitor Content_Specs":{"main":[[{"node":"Code: Prefilter & Exec ID","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Code: Prefilter & Exec ID":{"main":[[{"node":"IF: Should Process?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"IF: Should Process?":{"main":[[{"node":"Airtable: Get Last 10 Blog Topics","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Airtable: Update Rejected","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Airtable: Update Rejected":{"main":[[{"node":"Slack: Notify Rejection","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Structured Output Parser":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"AI Agent - Content Creator","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"AI Agent - Content Creator","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0},{"node":"Structured Output Parser","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Airtable: Get Last 10 Blog Top